findings.title: Deployer can lock/pause the contract
findings.description: The deployer has the ability to lock or pause the contract, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Deployer can set max transaction amount
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to set the maximum transaction amount.

findings.title: Deployer can set fees not more than 10%
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to set fees up to a maximum of 10%.
